text: Baza-Kuyanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Dyumeyevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 122 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo, 2 km from Berdyash. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Baza-Kuyanovo
